0.16 (practice in industry, although the model is very similar to current practice. Rather, the) 126 442 P
2.37 (model describes what it believed to be a good approach to machining, excluding) 126 428 P
-0.38 (feedback loops, which are desirable in the model, but have not been included on Figure) 126 414 P
(1. The OLPS system follows this model.) 126 400 T
