0.48 (Earlier versions of this library have included a tip condition which may be applied to) 126 361 P
0 (an end condition. For example, a hole could have a conical end, and then the tip of the) 126 347 P
1.09 (cone could be rounded. Earlier versions also included allowing a blend between the) 126 333 P
-0.31 (walls of the cylinder and the end, as well. For simplicity, no tip conditions are included) 126 319 P
